title: Ville Veier
overview: FlippKlipp Studio invites you to a crazy competition, where three celebrity teams are sent out in Oslo city center with the goal of performing as many embarrassing challenges as possible in one day. How far are they really willing to go for their teammates? With: Jonas Lihaug Fredriksen, Henrik Hildre, Hasse Hope, Markus Neby, Herman Flesvig and Maria Stavang.
